snippet.title: Armada Full Playthrough (All Endings)
snippet.description:
Game by Porpentine
Music by Ben Esposito, Neotenomie, Kodak Cameo, and Porpentine
Manual Art by Marras, Lilith, Porpentine, and Scott "Harmonyzone" McCloud

Released November 2nd, 2013 for Windows and Mac
Made with Game Maker

Play the game: https://xrafstar.monster/games/2d/armada/
Interview with the developer: https://www.giantbomb.com/articles/porpentine-s-wonderful-world-of-slime/1100-4847/

00:00 1st Playthrough
45:50 First Ending: Devoured
47:50 Menu Theme - Corporeal by Brenda Neotenomie
52:18 Path of Corruption
1:17:50 Second Ending: Handmaiden
1:19:30 2nd Playthrough
1:42:25 Third Ending: Escape
